      "title": "A slight increase in covid infected people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A slight increase in the number of Covid-infected people is currently being noted. According to the Government Information Department, 20 Covid-infected people were identified today.",
        "Accordingly, the number of Covid-infected people reported in Sri Lanka so far has increased to 664217."
